      Data: "Extra terrain generator instances (slots 1..N-1; slot 0 is terrainGenerator).
        Worldgen is ~100% async-GPU-readback-latency bound, so each extra generator
        lets one more column's readback be in flight concurrently. More generators
        \u2248 proportionally faster gen, until readbacks/CPU saturate. Each generator
        allocates its own column RTs (modest VRAM). Excluded from VRRefAssist injection
        ([Singleton] removed from McTerrainGenerator)."
